        GOOD_LUCK_I_WILL_BESTOW_UPON_YOU_YOUR                                = 7487,  -- Good luck, [citizen/comrade]. I will bestow upon you your nation's Signet.
        I_CANNOT_HELP_YOU_YOU_SHOULD_GO_FIND                                 = 7488,  -- I cannot help you. You should go find a guard from your own country.
        I_CANNOT_ACCEPT_CRYSTALS_FROM_SOMEONE_WHOSE_RANK                     = 7489,  -- I cannot accept crystals from someone whose rank is still 1. I advise you to either keep them until your reach rank 2, or to use them in craftwork.
