        IT_SHOULD_PLEASE_YOU_TO_KNOW_THAT_I                                  = 7571,  -- It should please you to know that I now also deal in %. Bigger pieces will earn you more points for your nation, and I'll even toss some gil into the equation!
        I_SEE_THAT_YOUR_HOME_COUNTRY_HAS_CONTROL                             = 7572,  -- I see that your home country has control of this region. Feel free to browse through my wares.
